<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>jạy yạ rby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - jạy yạ rby bạsjd lyk ʿnd rjlyk bạqdm ṭyby wnạrdyny
 wạn sẖkrt ạlʿmr klh msẖ hạ ykfy wlạ ạlạ̉bdyẗ hạ tkfyny
 1- zy sḥạbẗ mḥyt kẖṭạyạy bdmk dst ậtẖạmy wmạ hạ tdẖkrhạ tạny
 rḥt ạ̉htf byn ạlnạs wạ̉gẖny knt mdẖnb jyt kẖdt mkạny
 2- lmạ rfḍt ṭryqk wknt bạqwl lk ạ̉bʿd ʿny bnfsy ạkẖtrt hwạny
 mạ ʿạdsẖ ṭryqk hw ạlly yfrḥny knt mdẖnb jyt kẖdt mkạny
 3- mhmạ ạ̉gẖny bḥbk msẖ hạ ykfy wạ̉nạ bạsẖwf dmk bysyl ʿny
 kạn ṣlybk hw fdạỷy lạ̉ny knt mdẖnb jyt kẖdt mkạny</lyrics>
